<i>Military Police</i>
<i>reference blotter AR630.</i>

971
01:27:53,702 --> 01:27:56,970
Woman #2:
<i>Surveillance footage matches</i>
<i>visual of Joseph Smith.</i>

972
01:27:56,972 --> 01:27:59,506
Man #2:
<i>Department of Defense,</i>
<i>long-term missing person.</i>

973
01:27:59,508 --> 01:28:02,042
-  <i>Do you have a visual?</i>
