975
01:28:11,586 --> 01:28:14,955
<i>( audience applauding )</i>

976
01:29:18,586 --> 01:29:20,854
<i>( church bell ringing )</i>

977
01:29:33,468 --> 01:29:34,901
What are you doing here?

978
01:29:37,105 --> 01:29:39,039
I'm waiting
for Maria Zielinska.

979
01:29:41,576 --> 01:29:42,843
There was a party
after the show.

980
01:29:42,845 --> 01:29:44,010
I want to see her
walk to her car.

981
01:30:05,066 --> 01:30:06,833
Let me explain.

982
01:30:13,074 --> 01:30:14,908
When I'm sober...

983
01:30:18,079 --> 01:30:19,679
when I'm healthy
and well...

984
01:30:23,818 --> 01:30:25,519
I hurt people.

985
01:30:27,655 --> 01:30:29,623
<i>I'm lethal.</i>

986
01:30:31,659 --> 01:30:34,194
I drink to weaken
the machine they made.

987
01:30:38,032 --> 01:30:40,734
I've finished the work
I had to do.

988
01:30:55,183 --> 01:30:57,517
And already, look.

989
01:31:00,822 --> 01:31:01,922
You see 'em?

990
01:31:04,892 --> 01:31:06,960
Hummingbirds.

991
01:31:06,962 --> 01:31:09,596
<i>( hummingbird wings</i>
<i>fluttering )</i>

992
01:31:15,903 --> 01:31:18,939
Hummingbirds were there
that day.

993
01:31:18,941 --> 01:31:20,841
<i>( pilot's voice echoes )</i>

994
01:31:20,843 --> 01:31:23,677
<i>Do you copy?</i>

995
01:31:23,679 --> 01:31:27,514
Surveillance drones
saw what happened.

996
01:31:27,516 --> 01:31:29,149
Man on radio: <i>Roger that.</i>
<i>Hummingbird can see it.</i>

997
01:31:29,151 --> 01:31:30,851
<i>He's got a weapon...</i>

998
01:31:30,853 --> 01:31:33,553
<i>He's shooting up</i>
<i>in the air right now..</i>

999
01:31:33,555 --> 01:31:36,223
( yelling
in native language )

1000
01:31:41,095 --> 01:31:42,829
Please, please!

1001
01:31:44,999 --> 01:31:47,133
( screaming )

1002
01:31:49,036 --> 01:31:50,170
( choking )

1003
01:31:52,640 --> 01:31:54,841
The enemy killed
five of ours...

1004
01:32:02,250 --> 01:32:04,651
so I killed
five of theirs.

1005
01:32:07,989 --> 01:32:10,156
<i>The first five</i>
<i>I could find.</i>

1006
01:32:15,096 --> 01:32:17,864
I left the father
hanging.

1007
01:32:19,100 --> 01:32:20,734
<i>( gunfire )</i>

1008
01:32:23,638 --> 01:32:25,539
<i>( woman screams )</i>

1009
01:32:26,908 --> 01:32:29,809
( screaming )

1010
01:32:29,811 --> 01:32:31,912
( shouting
in native language )

1011
01:32:37,184 --> 01:32:39,252
<i>( screaming fades )</i>

1012
01:32:55,636 --> 01:32:59,039
<i>( footsteps approaching )</i>

1013
01:33:10,351 --> 01:33:11,918
You see her?

1014
01:33:14,689 --> 01:33:16,890
She is my witness.

1015
01:33:21,629 --> 01:33:22,996
<i>( car door closes )</i>

1016
01:34:04,205 --> 01:34:05,839
Sister.

1017
01:34:25,726 --> 01:34:27,894
Joey's voice:
<i>"Dear Cristina,</i>

1018
01:34:27,896 --> 01:34:31,665
<i>I just wanted to say thank you</i>
<i>for taking the photographs.</i>

1019
01:34:31,667 --> 01:34:32,899
<i>Considering it's me</i>
<i>in the pictures,</i>

1020
01:34:32,901 --> 01:34:36,269
<i>they turned out</i>
<i>pretty well.</i>

1021
01:34:36,271 --> 01:34:38,371
<i>I gave all the best ones</i>
<i>to my daughter,</i>

1022
01:34:38,373 --> 01:34:40,040
<i>so you're left</i>
<i>with the ugly ones</i>

1023
01:34:40,042 --> 01:34:42,809
<i>and the scary ones.</i>
<i>Sorry.</i>

1024
01:34:44,845 --> 01:34:46,746
<i>I've sent Damon the money</i>
<i>I took from his account</i>

1025
01:34:46,748 --> 01:34:48,715
<i>and added some extra</i>
<i>for rent.</i>

1026
01:34:50,751 --> 01:34:54,087
<i>I left the boys at the mission</i>
<i>some cash for pizzas.</i>

1027
01:34:54,089 --> 01:34:56,056
<i>And I sent details</i>
<i>of the people smugglers</i>

1028
01:34:56,058 --> 01:34:59,292
<i>to the police.</i>

1029
01:34:59,294 --> 01:35:01,828
<i>I also rid the city</i>
<i>of a bad man.</i>

1030
01:35:01,830 --> 01:35:04,164
<i>I know that doesn't</i>
<i>make me a good man,</i>

1031
01:35:04,166 --> 01:35:06,466
<i>but I tried to do</i>
<i>the right thing.</i>

1032
01:35:10,805 --> 01:35:13,440
<i>Now I'll go back to the street</i>
<i>and disappear.</i>

1033
01:35:13,442 --> 01:35:16,843
<i>I was alive again</i>
<i>for one summer.</i>

1034
01:35:16,845 --> 01:35:18,311
<i>I'm glad I spent it</i>
<i>with you.</i>

1035
01:35:20,448 --> 01:35:22,382
<i>I hope Africa</i>
<i>treats you well.</i>

1036
01:35:22,384 --> 01:35:25,151
<i>All my love,</i>
<i>Joseph Smith."</i>

1037
01:35:25,153 --> 01:35:27,220
<i>( sirens wailing )</i>

